Video-FFmpeg-FrameDecoder
======================================

This module attempts to provide a usable, high-level 
interface to reading video frames with FFmpeg.

This module requires FFmpeg development libraries, preferably >= 0.6


INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install


ACKNOWLEDGEMENTS

This library makes liberal use of code copied from Max Vohra's Video::FFmpeg 
and Martin Boehm's avcodec sample application.


